# Quality Checklist

## Before Committing

- [ ] Tests written FIRST and passing
- [ ] Both feature flag paths tested (if applicable)
- [ ] Linter passes (`npm run lint` or `dotnet build`)
- [ ] All controllers have `[Authorize]`
- [ ] Error responses use 502 for downstream errors
- [ ] Task tracker updated
- [ ] No secrets committed
- [ ] `X-Correlation-Id` header propagated (backend)
